    "one_line_summary": "The Tamil Nadu Health Department has initiated a vaccination and health screening drive for children and senior citizens.",
    "confirmed_facts": [
      "The state health department launched a special vaccination and health screening drive on July 3.",
      "The drive is aimed at children and senior citizens across government hospitals and primary health centres.",
      "The campaign will focus on routine childhood vaccination, diabetes screening, blood pressure checks, and basic health counselling for elderly residents.",
      "Mobile medical teams will visit selected rural and semi-urban areas.",
      "Health workers will identify children who missed scheduled vaccines and encourage parents to complete pending doses.",
      "Senior citizens will be screened for common lifestyle-related conditions and referred to higher medical centres if needed.",
      "The drive is preventive in nature and not linked to any disease outbreak.",
      "The drive will continue for two weeks.",
      "Local health officials have been asked to submit daily reports on attendance, referrals, and medicine availability."
